WEBVTT

01:52.900 --> 01:57.350
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.650 --> 02:01.900
[Episode 19]

02:09.300 --> 02:11.520
[Latrine]

02:16.270 --> 02:18.000
-Let's do this!
-Let's do this!

02:19.220 --> 02:22.180
[Latrine]

02:40.740 --> 02:41.700
Fan Yun,

02:41.730 --> 02:43.760
can you really discern so many nuances?

02:43.760 --> 02:45.230
How is that possible?

02:45.250 --> 02:46.570
I just made it up.

02:46.600 --> 02:48.600
As long as everyone enjoys the food.

03:22.870 --> 03:25.000
Fan Yun is still cleaning the latrine?

03:26.250 --> 03:27.440
Poor thing.

03:27.460 --> 03:28.720
It's been half a month.

04:02.110 --> 04:03.280
This is...

04:23.600 --> 04:25.570
Academician Tian really got unlucky.

04:25.570 --> 04:27.100
He came in first in the exam,

04:27.510 --> 04:30.370
yet he's been sweeping the courtyard
all this time.

04:32.560 --> 04:33.970
The mentor is Lord Lu.

04:34.670 --> 04:36.600
There's nothing he can do about it.

04:36.930 --> 04:40.060
It's like this for every cohort.
There's no escaping it.

04:42.820 --> 04:43.870
But I believe

04:44.480 --> 04:46.240
those with true potential

04:46.480 --> 04:47.990
will make it through.

04:49.430 --> 04:50.580
I believe in Fan Yun.

04:51.430 --> 04:52.430
I believe in them.

04:55.600 --> 04:56.480
So,

04:56.860 --> 04:58.860
before Fan Yun and Academician Tian

04:59.360 --> 05:00.730
enter the storehouse,

05:01.720 --> 05:02.750
take these

05:02.750 --> 05:04.700
unfinished documents we've sorted out

05:04.700 --> 05:06.430
and add them to their workload.

05:07.180 --> 05:08.860
I remember that they

05:08.890 --> 05:11.550
clean the latrine and courtyard
in the morning,

05:11.720 --> 05:12.750
and sort books

05:13.450 --> 05:15.430
in the storehouse in the afternoon.

05:15.430 --> 05:16.320
Are you trying

05:16.990 --> 05:18.660
to add insult to injury?

05:19.950 --> 05:21.430
We're also overwhelmed.

05:21.910 --> 05:22.930
How about...

05:24.950 --> 05:26.090
you do these then?

05:28.350 --> 05:29.360
I'll go right now.

05:40.850 --> 05:41.820
Lord Cai.

05:42.990 --> 05:43.950
Lord Yan.

05:44.420 --> 05:45.659
Any problems?

05:47.280 --> 05:49.480
There is a problem indeed.

05:50.000 --> 05:51.310
You're responsible

05:51.310 --> 05:53.920
for mentoring newly appointed officials,

05:53.920 --> 05:54.830
right?

05:54.830 --> 05:55.800
That's right.

05:57.080 --> 05:58.150
Look at

05:58.190 --> 06:00.450
Fan Yun and Tian Xing's situation now.

06:00.760 --> 06:02.810
Their workload keeps increasing.

06:03.090 --> 06:05.570
Don't you have anything to say about this?

06:07.740 --> 06:08.910
So,

06:08.940 --> 06:11.130
this is what you're curious about.

06:13.430 --> 06:14.630
Lord Yan,

06:14.920 --> 06:15.600
with this matter,

06:15.600 --> 06:17.650
complaining to me won't help.

06:18.270 --> 06:20.820
Lord Lu's the one
who assigned them the tasks.

06:21.200 --> 06:23.100
Many people were present then.

06:23.700 --> 06:26.440
I couldn't have intervened,
as that'd make Lord Lu seem

06:26.440 --> 06:28.650
so wavering and indecisive in his actions;

06:28.650 --> 06:29.870
don't you agree?

06:32.760 --> 06:33.800
However,

06:33.830 --> 06:36.230
you're not the first one
to plead for them.

06:38.270 --> 06:39.159
What do you mean?

06:39.159 --> 06:40.560
Your father, Lord Fan Hui,

06:40.560 --> 06:42.950
also came to me about Fan Yun,

06:42.950 --> 06:44.720
hoping I could transfer her.

06:46.120 --> 06:47.710
But back then,

06:47.870 --> 06:48.880
didn't you

06:49.020 --> 06:51.090
shovel horse manure too?

06:51.120 --> 06:52.440
I never saw Lord Fan

06:52.460 --> 06:54.630
come to plead for you.

06:55.470 --> 06:56.390
In the end,

06:57.530 --> 07:00.120
I guess blood is thicker than water.

07:00.650 --> 07:02.230
My father treats me very well.

07:02.230 --> 07:03.870
That's for sure.

07:04.200 --> 07:06.010
Even though you're adopted,

07:06.030 --> 07:07.510
I believe Lord Fan

07:07.540 --> 07:09.950
surely treats you equally.

07:10.610 --> 07:13.250
Not to mention he has no son of his own.

07:13.270 --> 07:15.420
You didn't inherit the Fan surname,

07:15.450 --> 07:17.510
but you're still considered family.

07:19.980 --> 07:21.100
Lord Yan,

07:21.680 --> 07:23.060
Lord Fan is

07:23.600 --> 07:25.440
fickle and ruthless.

07:26.120 --> 07:28.680
It wouldn't be surprising

07:29.050 --> 07:30.580
if he abandons you some day.

07:31.520 --> 07:33.710
I highly value your talent.

07:33.880 --> 07:36.270
I'd never do the same thing as him.

07:36.390 --> 07:38.000
If you become independent one day,

07:38.000 --> 07:39.400
-I believe...
-Lord Cai.

07:40.180 --> 07:41.300
I have things to do.

07:41.780 --> 07:42.570
Excuse me.

08:16.360 --> 08:17.270
Kid,

08:17.420 --> 08:19.020
I'd like to buy some flowers.

08:20.730 --> 08:21.340
Here.

08:22.240 --> 08:23.800
Here are your flowers.

08:27.560 --> 08:29.000
These pear blossoms

08:29.020 --> 08:31.090
aren't worth much.

08:31.270 --> 08:33.299
This is quite a lucrative business.

08:33.929 --> 08:35.169
Was it...

08:36.539 --> 08:38.539
your parents who gave you this idea?

08:38.710 --> 08:39.909
I don't have parents.

08:40.100 --> 08:41.360
No one takes care of me.

08:41.679 --> 08:43.880
But I still have to find a way to survive.

08:50.760 --> 08:52.120
You're it.

08:53.050 --> 08:54.130
Me?

08:57.700 --> 08:59.620
When you took me in,

09:00.950 --> 09:02.620
it was probably just on a whim.

09:04.980 --> 09:07.440
Just like picking up a stray dog
to take home.

09:16.870 --> 09:17.480
Father.

09:19.820 --> 09:21.520
What are you standing here for?

09:21.520 --> 09:22.650
Why are you in a daze?

09:23.020 --> 09:23.780
No,

09:24.130 --> 09:26.660
I was just admiring
the flowers and greenery.

09:27.030 --> 09:27.910
You, however,

09:28.550 --> 09:30.760
don't look very happy.

09:31.270 --> 09:32.060
Do I?

09:33.560 --> 09:34.300
Not at all.

09:36.040 --> 09:37.970
But you; is something on your mind?

09:39.270 --> 09:40.510
No, nothing.

09:42.670 --> 09:43.600
Alright.

09:45.480 --> 09:47.590
There are a few old fogeys
in the Services Bureau

09:47.590 --> 09:49.750
who are still stuck in their old ways.

09:50.840 --> 09:52.550
I guess I have no choice but to

09:52.550 --> 09:54.060
expel them from Qi Residence.

09:54.060 --> 09:55.060
Father.

09:56.910 --> 09:57.840
What is it?

09:58.270 --> 09:59.030
I have

09:59.790 --> 10:00.950
a question for you.

10:03.400 --> 10:04.400
If I plan

10:04.510 --> 10:05.750
to leave you

10:06.320 --> 10:09.160
to wander around the Nine Cities
to cultivate my mind,

10:09.160 --> 10:10.010
what...

10:11.170 --> 10:12.240
would you think?

10:12.310 --> 10:13.400
Wander around?

10:15.400 --> 10:17.740
With your terrible sense of direction,

10:18.680 --> 10:20.280
how'd you find your way back?

10:23.700 --> 10:25.030
Don't worry about that.

10:26.030 --> 10:26.950
I have my ways.

10:29.770 --> 10:30.770
Fine.

10:31.070 --> 10:32.380
Go if you want.

10:33.730 --> 10:35.280
It's your life;

10:35.300 --> 10:36.780
you make the call.

10:56.470 --> 10:59.570
[Huiyun Pavilion]

10:58.240 --> 10:59.310
If I'd like you to

10:59.980 --> 11:02.710
come back to the Guardian Corps,
are you willing?

11:05.120 --> 11:06.120
Your Excellency,

11:06.210 --> 11:07.930
I only came back before

11:08.200 --> 11:09.430
for an emergency.

11:09.920 --> 11:10.870
But if...

11:10.890 --> 11:12.290
I have my considerations

11:13.360 --> 11:14.680
for wanting you back.

11:18.910 --> 11:21.560
Fan Yun has just become
a probationary civil official.

11:21.560 --> 11:23.260
Studying and training alone in here

11:23.260 --> 11:24.430
is a kind of hardship

11:25.550 --> 11:27.070
she's never experienced.

11:29.790 --> 11:31.910
Fan Yun isn't as fragile as we think.

11:32.480 --> 11:33.270
I believe

11:33.290 --> 11:34.890
she can take on any challenge

11:35.360 --> 11:36.790
and stick to her goals

11:36.790 --> 11:37.990
until the end.

11:38.390 --> 11:39.380
I know she doesn't

11:39.380 --> 11:41.040
need anyone's help right now.

11:41.080 --> 11:43.000
But now, she and Tian Xing;

11:43.720 --> 11:45.150
one is a probationary civil official,

11:45.150 --> 11:47.280
and the other a commoner academician.

11:47.970 --> 11:49.540
Their current situation is

11:51.270 --> 11:52.930
more perilous than you think.

11:58.230 --> 12:00.030
What does Your Excellency mean?

12:05.130 --> 12:07.190
We must always prepare for the worst.

12:09.630 --> 12:10.960
On one hand, I want you

12:11.350 --> 12:12.900
to come back to protect her.

12:13.750 --> 12:15.000
On the other hand,

12:16.090 --> 12:17.520
knowing you're nearby

12:18.090 --> 12:19.890
to look out for her,

12:20.200 --> 12:21.600
she'll feel more secure.

12:26.750 --> 12:28.210
Thank you for your understanding.

12:28.210 --> 12:30.610
I'm willing to
stay here and accompany her.

12:32.030 --> 12:33.000
That's good.

12:37.790 --> 12:39.070
Actually,

12:40.070 --> 12:42.000
it's not just Fan Yun who needs you.

12:43.670 --> 12:45.070
The Nine Cities need you.

12:45.870 --> 12:47.080
I need you too.

13:00.090 --> 13:01.600
I understand.

13:17.680 --> 13:19.010
I wonder if

13:19.030 --> 13:21.290
Dad and the others have been eating well.

13:21.630 --> 13:22.550
What's wrong?

13:22.790 --> 13:23.750
Homesick?

13:30.270 --> 13:30.910
Fan Yun.

13:33.540 --> 13:35.850
Gao Ran! What brings you here?

13:35.880 --> 13:37.010
I finally found you.

13:37.270 --> 13:38.460
Are you reinstated?

13:39.680 --> 13:41.010
Let's sit down and talk.

13:44.300 --> 13:45.700
While I wasn't here,

13:45.730 --> 13:46.930
did anyone bully you?

13:49.030 --> 13:50.480
Who'd dare to bully me?

13:51.330 --> 13:52.300
True.

13:52.730 --> 13:53.560
But if you ever

13:53.580 --> 13:55.090
reach your breaking point,

13:55.090 --> 13:56.020
always remember

13:56.140 --> 13:58.220
that Lord Fan Qi and I are behind you.

13:58.870 --> 13:59.730
I know.

13:59.950 --> 14:01.220
Don't worry.

14:01.250 --> 14:03.610
Look, Tian Xing and I are doing just fine.

14:04.900 --> 14:06.470
We help each other out.

14:06.800 --> 14:09.000
It's a bit tiring, but very fulfilling.

14:10.890 --> 14:11.610
Right.

14:11.650 --> 14:13.460
I brought letters for you two.

14:20.900 --> 14:22.120
Miss Wei?

14:22.140 --> 14:23.110
Miss Wei?

14:29.160 --> 14:30.560
It's a letter from her.

14:31.470 --> 14:33.190
Why are you so nervous?

14:35.960 --> 14:37.120
Oh...

14:38.300 --> 14:39.610
W-What does it say?

14:39.640 --> 14:42.300
She said her mother
arranged a marriage for her,

14:42.570 --> 14:43.940
rushing her to go home.

14:44.200 --> 14:46.110
She didn't have time to tell me in person,

14:46.110 --> 14:47.310
so she wrote a letter.

14:47.480 --> 14:48.180
A marriage?

14:51.190 --> 14:52.320
Don't you forget me.

14:53.310 --> 14:54.070
Right.

14:54.590 --> 14:56.830
I think she once mentioned to me

14:56.860 --> 14:59.790
that she was old friends with that man.

15:00.770 --> 15:02.290
What was his name...

15:02.970 --> 15:04.800
Sima something.

15:04.930 --> 15:06.070
Sima?

15:08.090 --> 15:11.040
That doesn't sound like a noble's name.

15:12.590 --> 15:13.800
How did they meet?

15:17.360 --> 15:18.820
Did she say anything else?

15:19.340 --> 15:20.460
Nothing else.

15:20.490 --> 15:22.350
She said she'll be back soon.

15:24.410 --> 15:25.570
What's wrong?

15:26.090 --> 15:27.150
Worried about her?

15:27.870 --> 15:28.650
No.

15:29.800 --> 15:31.940
Just glad it's quiet now.

15:44.160 --> 15:45.560
What's wrong, Tian Xing?

15:47.550 --> 15:49.790
Zhu Luan's letter says
she didn't receive

15:49.790 --> 15:52.450
the academician's congratulatory gold
I sent.

15:53.910 --> 15:55.440
Who did you give the gold to?

15:57.670 --> 15:58.870
The Services Bureau.

16:04.320 --> 16:05.670
The Services Bureau?

16:07.220 --> 16:10.300
[Spare No Effort to Be
Loyal, Honest, and Kind]

16:14.750 --> 16:16.060
Is that so?

16:17.340 --> 16:19.420
I just received a letter from Yong City,

16:19.420 --> 16:20.880
saying that the congratulatory gold

16:20.880 --> 16:22.200
entrusted to the Services Bureau

16:22.200 --> 16:23.660
hasn't been received yet.

16:23.820 --> 16:25.840
I wonder what went wrong.

16:29.030 --> 16:31.240
What could go wrong?

16:33.610 --> 16:35.250
The one in charge of

16:36.470 --> 16:38.470
the academician's congratulatory gold

16:38.470 --> 16:39.830
is Lord Lu.

16:40.890 --> 16:42.080
Lord Lu,

16:42.110 --> 16:43.360
what's going on?

16:44.970 --> 16:46.680
Right, right.

16:47.600 --> 16:48.670
Well,

16:48.670 --> 16:50.800
I know about Academician Tian's gold.

16:51.150 --> 16:52.530
It's already been sent out.

16:52.530 --> 16:54.810
It's probably just a long journey.

16:55.590 --> 16:56.930
Wait a few more days.

16:59.020 --> 17:00.220
But the express horse

17:00.440 --> 17:01.550
delivering the good news

17:01.550 --> 17:03.600
went to Yong City with the gold.

17:04.579 --> 17:05.490
Why did

17:05.839 --> 17:07.010
the news arrive,

17:07.550 --> 17:09.000
but not the gold?

17:10.310 --> 17:11.920
Lord Lu already said

17:11.920 --> 17:13.359
it's a long journey.

17:13.520 --> 17:15.420
Just wait a few more days.

17:15.670 --> 17:17.270
Go back and wait.

17:17.290 --> 17:18.270
You may leave.

17:18.790 --> 17:19.310
But I...

17:19.310 --> 17:20.440
We understand.

17:21.790 --> 17:22.770
Thank you, My Lord.

17:22.770 --> 17:24.640
We'll wait a few more days.

17:28.210 --> 17:29.340
Let's go, Tian Xing.

17:43.790 --> 17:44.490
Come.

17:48.240 --> 17:49.640
They were being evasive.

17:49.880 --> 17:51.120
I think there is

17:51.140 --> 17:52.470
more than meets the eye.

17:52.920 --> 17:54.000
Will the gold

17:54.550 --> 17:56.080
really arrive in a few days?

17:57.630 --> 18:00.020
A few days early or late isn't important.

18:00.160 --> 18:01.020
But I'm afraid

18:01.360 --> 18:04.020
someone in Services Bureau
is being dishonest.

18:05.420 --> 18:06.280
Let's go first.

18:31.810 --> 18:34.680
Lord Gao Ran, are you OK?

18:37.840 --> 18:38.720
I'm fine.

18:39.350 --> 18:41.320
It's just my first time

18:41.340 --> 18:42.820
finding the Qi Residence

18:43.550 --> 18:44.810
so empty.

18:51.910 --> 18:52.570
Assassins!

18:52.600 --> 18:54.260
Quick, protect the governor!

18:56.710 --> 18:57.710
Your Excellency!

18:58.460 --> 18:59.910
You, you! You drink.

19:05.920 --> 19:06.990
Stand down.

19:08.900 --> 19:10.960
So Your Excellency is
feasting with the two lords.

19:10.960 --> 19:12.900
I won't disturb you. Pardon me.

19:13.030 --> 19:14.380
Impressive, Yan Jiang.

19:14.770 --> 19:15.900
With a little trick,

19:16.040 --> 19:17.690
he lured Gao Ran here.

19:19.330 --> 19:20.020
Wait!

19:21.460 --> 19:22.420
Gao Ran,

19:22.760 --> 19:23.880
since you're here,

19:24.060 --> 19:25.630
sit down and have a drink.

19:25.770 --> 19:26.730
Unwind for once.

19:26.760 --> 19:27.650
Exactly.

19:28.870 --> 19:30.620
I'm on duty. I can't drink.

19:32.240 --> 19:33.050
Wei, Yan.

19:35.290 --> 19:36.550
-Come, come.
-Come on.

19:38.210 --> 19:39.540
Lord Gao Ran,

19:39.570 --> 19:40.560
come on.

19:40.770 --> 19:41.600
Come, come.

19:41.650 --> 19:42.650
Sit.

19:42.680 --> 19:44.680
I'll hold on to this for you.

19:47.850 --> 19:50.330
Gao Ran disturbed Your Excellency.

19:50.350 --> 19:51.810
Shouldn't he be punished?

19:52.540 --> 19:54.000
Yes, he should be punished.

19:54.000 --> 19:55.440
At least 3 cups.

19:56.680 --> 19:57.880
Plus my cup.

19:57.900 --> 19:58.960
Five cups in total.

19:59.040 --> 20:00.040
Your Excellency,

20:00.320 --> 20:01.210
you miscalculated.

20:01.210 --> 20:02.490
How could it be 5 cups?

20:03.500 --> 20:04.220
Right.

20:04.510 --> 20:05.470
Six cups.

20:06.480 --> 20:07.350
No.

20:07.350 --> 20:08.440
Add another 3 cups.

20:08.440 --> 20:09.470
Ten cups in total.

20:10.080 --> 20:11.600
Then Gao Ran, come.

20:11.930 --> 20:13.010
Down this pot.

20:27.470 --> 20:29.360
-You sure can drink!
-Bravo!

20:31.740 --> 20:32.810
Not bad.

20:42.680 --> 20:44.440
Why is Your Excellency sighing?

20:44.440 --> 20:45.810
Something bothering you?

20:45.810 --> 20:48.030
Vent to us so we can have a laugh.

20:51.880 --> 20:52.580
Well,

20:53.750 --> 20:54.960
seeing Gao Ran

20:55.920 --> 20:57.120
reminds me of Fan Yun.

20:58.000 --> 20:59.160
Fan Yun has entered the estate

20:59.160 --> 21:00.160
to be an official,

21:00.820 --> 21:03.350
but she's still cleaning the latrine
every day.

21:03.350 --> 21:05.280
She's suffered so much injustice.

21:06.400 --> 21:07.440
I just feel like

21:08.090 --> 21:10.130
she's still so far out of reach.

21:11.850 --> 21:13.090
No way.

21:13.120 --> 21:14.800
The estate is only this big.

21:14.820 --> 21:15.940
It's not like

21:15.970 --> 21:17.400
Your Excellency is like Yan Jiang,

21:17.400 --> 21:18.600
getting lost in here.

21:19.290 --> 21:20.820
What does it have to do with me?

21:20.820 --> 21:24.040
You're the supreme governor.
Just go see whoever you want.

21:24.040 --> 21:25.220
As you all know,

21:25.720 --> 21:27.160
seeking an official position,

21:27.160 --> 21:28.960
what could Fan Yun want the most?

21:29.030 --> 21:30.510
It's a free and fair

21:30.510 --> 21:31.870
path to officialdom.

21:32.550 --> 21:33.540
As the governor,

21:33.710 --> 21:34.870
I have to hold back.

21:35.440 --> 21:37.640
I can't say or do anything to intervene!

21:38.350 --> 21:39.550
Fan Yun is her father's

21:39.550 --> 21:40.690
little princess.

21:40.860 --> 21:41.660
In the estate,

21:41.680 --> 21:45.240
Your Excellency is
so intuitive and considerate.

21:45.510 --> 21:47.310
As the adopted son of the Fans,

21:48.060 --> 21:49.860
I'm a bit jealous of this sister.

21:50.060 --> 21:53.260
Sister. Sister. Sister. Sister! Sister!

21:53.290 --> 21:55.990
Just hearing the word "sister"
gives me a headache.

21:55.990 --> 21:57.470
Our Wei Shisan

21:57.500 --> 21:59.380
acts crazy all day long.

22:00.000 --> 22:01.500
She went back for a blind date,

22:01.500 --> 22:02.830
but I don't know if

22:02.850 --> 22:04.890
she'll get along with that Sima Xun.

22:05.820 --> 22:08.350
Well, at least I have
some peace and quiet now.

22:24.160 --> 22:25.760
Why are you all looking at me?

22:26.270 --> 22:28.430
This is all related to you!

22:28.450 --> 22:29.730
How is it related to me?

22:30.240 --> 22:31.690
I'm all alone now,

22:32.010 --> 22:33.760
but you get to be with Fan Yun
all the time.

22:33.760 --> 22:34.070
I...

22:34.070 --> 22:35.400
Shisan is infatuated with you,

22:35.400 --> 22:36.510
but you ignore her.

22:36.510 --> 22:37.310
Don't think I don't know!

22:37.310 --> 22:38.200
If it weren't for you,

22:38.200 --> 22:40.460
I wouldn't have been adopted by the Fans!

22:40.760 --> 22:41.760
Wait.

22:42.370 --> 22:44.680
I admit
what the governor and Lord Wei said,

22:44.680 --> 22:45.720
but what does your adoption

22:45.720 --> 22:47.070
have to do with me?

22:48.710 --> 22:50.120
That traces back to

22:50.140 --> 22:52.100
my ignorant youth.

22:54.000 --> 22:55.070
I was adopted

22:55.070 --> 22:56.990
by the Fans around 13 years ago.

22:57.540 --> 22:58.400
Think about it.

22:58.720 --> 22:59.880
Back then, what happened

22:59.880 --> 23:01.210
in Lord Fan Qi's family?

23:01.380 --> 23:02.520
Father must have been thinking,

23:02.520 --> 23:03.930
"I heard my brother

23:03.960 --> 23:05.420
recently adopted a boy.

23:05.820 --> 23:08.410
I want to experience
that kind of hardship too.

23:08.410 --> 23:09.720
Let's pick a good time

23:09.740 --> 23:10.980
to adopt one."

23:12.490 --> 23:13.880
That must be it!

23:14.700 --> 23:16.700
I just happened to catch his eye!

23:17.170 --> 23:18.010
So...

23:18.790 --> 23:20.120
Whatever. Let's drink!

23:20.830 --> 23:22.350
Hey, stop drinking.

23:25.340 --> 23:26.160
Send him back.

23:26.160 --> 23:27.220
I'll take you back.

23:27.250 --> 23:27.810
No more drinking.

23:27.810 --> 23:28.830
-Let's go back.
-Let's play games!

23:28.830 --> 23:30.230
-Go on!
-Enough already.

23:30.480 --> 23:31.290
Is he OK?

23:31.660 --> 23:32.500
He's fine.

23:32.520 --> 23:33.920
I'll take him back first.

23:34.040 --> 23:34.750
-Drink.
-You,

23:34.750 --> 23:37.480
take this chance
to have a talk with the governor.

23:37.860 --> 23:39.000
-Alright.
-Let's play games!

23:39.000 --> 23:40.030
Let's play when we get home, OK?

23:40.030 --> 23:41.070
Lord Yan.

23:41.750 --> 23:43.080
-Fine, fine.
-Let's go.

23:44.130 --> 23:45.900
If he saw me again, do you think

23:45.930 --> 23:47.570
he'd still take me in?

23:47.590 --> 23:48.630
No, he wouldn't!

23:48.660 --> 23:50.060
I'll stand up for you, OK?

23:50.210 --> 23:52.280
-I know the way.
-Careful on the stairs.

23:52.280 --> 23:53.450
Oh my goodness.

23:54.160 --> 23:55.510
This way? Or this way?

23:55.850 --> 23:57.250
-This way.
-Oh, this way.

23:59.620 --> 24:01.750
Even Lord Yan gets this drunk.

24:04.140 --> 24:05.140
Your Excellency.

24:06.520 --> 24:07.280
Are you OK?

24:18.240 --> 24:18.960
Brother,

24:20.920 --> 24:22.850
I want to share something with you,

24:25.190 --> 24:27.080
but you can't tell anyone.

24:30.190 --> 24:31.040
Go on.

24:32.590 --> 24:34.920
When Fan Yun was my wife,

24:35.290 --> 24:37.810
she shared a lot of my burdens.

24:39.490 --> 24:41.520
Now she works so hard...

24:43.230 --> 24:45.160
but I can't help her with anything.

24:47.860 --> 24:49.130
I feel so useless.

24:50.760 --> 24:52.090
I really, really want to

24:52.120 --> 24:53.450
do something for her.

24:55.140 --> 24:56.590
I just feel so useless.

25:04.470 --> 25:06.070
It's good enough that you are

25:06.330 --> 25:07.790
protecting her in secret.

25:07.980 --> 25:10.310
When Fan Yun's official career takes off,

25:10.560 --> 25:13.420
she'll still need
Your Excellency's full support.

25:17.790 --> 25:18.490
At least,

25:19.850 --> 25:20.890
you've done

25:22.220 --> 25:24.260
far more than I have.

25:30.350 --> 25:31.110
Alright.

25:31.560 --> 25:32.620
I'll get going too.

25:32.840 --> 25:34.080
Rest early.

25:36.010 --> 25:38.200
I'm always on your side, Brother.

25:39.920 --> 25:41.450
I'm always on your side too.

25:48.430 --> 25:50.830
I'm finally almost done sorting these out.

25:50.830 --> 25:53.300
Tian Xing,
I'll deliver the documents first.

25:53.300 --> 25:54.430
OK, I'll go inside.

25:58.770 --> 26:00.170
There's a tray today too.

26:06.120 --> 26:07.470
It's Longquan tea.

26:07.930 --> 26:09.260
It relieves fatigue.

26:09.570 --> 26:11.170
I don't know who sent it,

26:11.550 --> 26:13.030
but it's delivered daily.

26:13.750 --> 26:14.750
How thoughtful.

26:17.850 --> 26:19.760
Tian Xing,
I'll deliver the documents now.

26:19.760 --> 26:20.710
Go inside.

26:20.730 --> 26:21.860
OK, I'll bring it in.

26:24.850 --> 26:25.890
Be careful.

26:39.400 --> 26:40.710
Fan... Fan Yun.

26:42.770 --> 26:43.840
I'll bring more.

26:44.430 --> 26:44.850
OK.

26:57.490 --> 26:58.290
I'll help you.

27:06.370 --> 27:07.370
Your Excellency?

27:09.960 --> 27:10.960
Your Excellency?

27:11.470 --> 27:12.180
You...

27:13.820 --> 27:14.860
Your Excellency,

27:15.680 --> 27:16.890
why are you here?

27:17.890 --> 27:19.130
Here's the thing.

27:19.210 --> 27:20.610
I was going to go in and help,

27:20.610 --> 27:21.430
but I'm amazing;

27:21.430 --> 27:22.660
I know the big picture.

27:22.660 --> 27:24.260
I knew I couldn't take that step,

27:24.260 --> 27:25.390
so I held back.

27:25.410 --> 27:26.550
As I was about to leave,

27:26.550 --> 27:27.290
you spotted me.

27:27.290 --> 27:28.320
That is all.

27:32.070 --> 27:32.830
But...

27:33.590 --> 27:34.630
held what back?

27:36.450 --> 27:37.210
Nothing.

27:38.140 --> 27:39.670
I'm really just passing by.

27:39.880 --> 27:41.310
I didn't plan to
ask how your work was going,

27:41.310 --> 27:42.170
if you had dinner,

27:42.170 --> 27:43.510
or bring you any food.

27:45.050 --> 27:45.620
I'm off.

27:50.170 --> 27:51.570
You didn't do anything,

27:52.510 --> 27:53.160
but

27:53.960 --> 27:55.360
I still want to thank you!

28:10.680 --> 28:12.250
I, Fan Yun, am here.

28:12.280 --> 28:13.480
I, Tian Xing, am here.

28:18.090 --> 28:19.890
Have you two finished your work?

28:20.460 --> 28:21.180
Almost.

28:21.200 --> 28:21.860
Nearly.

28:22.580 --> 28:24.710
Almost? Nearly?

28:25.520 --> 28:27.640
Your work isn't finished,
and you're even late?

28:27.640 --> 28:28.400
I've given you so much time...

28:28.400 --> 28:28.890
My Lord.

28:33.830 --> 28:34.890
What are you doing?

28:35.030 --> 28:37.590
My Lord, they've stayed up late for days

28:37.610 --> 28:39.030
and are utterly exhausted.

28:39.030 --> 28:42.030
Could you allow them to
take a brief rest in the lounge?

28:43.240 --> 28:44.310
Bo Qin,

28:45.440 --> 28:47.500
did the sun rise from the west today?

28:47.860 --> 28:49.320
Speaking up for them, huh?

28:50.270 --> 28:51.310
Then are you going to

28:51.310 --> 28:52.990
clean the latrine and sort the documents?

28:52.990 --> 28:54.080
I'll do it for them.

28:54.100 --> 28:55.380
I'll take that as a yes.

28:55.410 --> 28:57.960
Thank you, My Lord. Let's go.

29:02.430 --> 29:04.320
You two just rest up here.

29:10.720 --> 29:11.900
Bo Qin, thank you.

29:14.480 --> 29:15.200
Bo,

29:15.790 --> 29:18.190
you used to be so hostile to us.

29:18.720 --> 29:20.030
Why've you been

29:20.030 --> 29:22.050
standing up for us time and again lately?

29:22.050 --> 29:23.580
I'm not doing it for you.
I just don't want

29:23.580 --> 29:24.800
others to be inconvenienced

29:24.800 --> 29:26.660
if you collapse from exhaustion.

29:26.920 --> 29:27.780
Get some sleep.

29:30.930 --> 29:32.410
Did... Did he

29:32.960 --> 29:34.160
find his conscience?

29:34.530 --> 29:36.260
He changed his tune so quickly.

29:41.270 --> 29:41.950
Alright.

29:42.210 --> 29:43.600
Since that's the case,

29:43.830 --> 29:45.990
his kind intentions shouldn't go to waste.

29:45.990 --> 29:47.280
Let's take a rest.

30:11.160 --> 30:12.480
The Services Bureau's expenses have

30:12.480 --> 30:13.940
always been astronomical.

30:13.940 --> 30:15.980
How's it even more outrageous this year?

30:15.980 --> 30:16.700
This...

30:19.240 --> 30:21.440
All the daily necessities in the estate

30:21.790 --> 30:24.460
have always been purchased
by the Services Bureau.

30:24.460 --> 30:26.060
This is indeed a gravy train.

30:26.590 --> 30:29.850
It's inevitable that someone
will line their own pockets.

30:30.480 --> 30:33.610
Do you want to order an investigation,
Your Excellency?

30:43.160 --> 30:46.420
Then I'll have to trouble you
to visit the Services Bureau.

30:49.290 --> 30:50.610
You two plug your ears.

30:55.700 --> 30:57.590
You can let Fan Yun investigate.

30:59.650 --> 31:00.900
You mean to

31:00.930 --> 31:02.330
let Fan Yun investigate?

31:03.200 --> 31:04.860
But her words carry no weight,

31:05.160 --> 31:07.600
and her being recommended as an official

31:07.620 --> 31:09.050
has invited much gossip.

31:09.080 --> 31:10.480
Exactly because of this,

31:10.710 --> 31:13.020
she needs a chance to prove herself.

31:13.570 --> 31:15.180
Rather than being punished all day,

31:15.180 --> 31:16.770
why don't she take the initiative to

31:16.770 --> 31:17.870
prove her capability?

31:17.870 --> 31:19.750
Besides, I believe

31:20.070 --> 31:22.270
Fan Yun is the most suitable candidate.

31:23.350 --> 31:24.800
As for experience,

31:25.400 --> 31:27.530
she'll have it once she gets this done.

31:27.740 --> 31:28.710
So I think

31:28.970 --> 31:30.500
this is the right decision.

31:34.640 --> 31:35.770
I understand.

31:44.180 --> 31:45.220
Your Excellency,

31:45.240 --> 31:47.700
how'd you know
about Fan Yun being punished?

31:49.050 --> 31:50.130
I...

31:53.200 --> 31:54.460
I hope Your Excellency

31:54.760 --> 31:56.530
attends more to government affairs,

31:56.530 --> 31:58.460
-I…
-instead of wandering around.

32:21.200 --> 32:22.300
After the rest,

32:22.320 --> 32:23.720
I do feel more energetic.

32:24.460 --> 32:26.460
Tian Xing, let's work harder today.

32:27.040 --> 32:28.290
-OK...
-Tonight,

32:28.590 --> 32:30.510
we must sort out

32:30.610 --> 32:31.810
all these documents.

32:32.200 --> 32:34.240
Why is there a ledger here?

32:35.310 --> 32:36.110
Fan Yun.

32:38.390 --> 32:39.390
Look at this.

32:38.390 --> 32:41.700
[Ledger]

32:42.960 --> 32:43.960
A ledger?

32:45.920 --> 32:46.570
This is...

32:48.010 --> 32:49.740
the Services Bureau's ledger?

33:13.610 --> 33:14.410
Tian Xing,

33:14.930 --> 33:16.280
there really is a problem

33:16.280 --> 33:17.340
with their ledger.

33:18.480 --> 33:19.280
What problem?

33:21.190 --> 33:21.880
Look.

33:22.170 --> 33:23.860
Among these everyday items,

33:23.890 --> 33:25.570
some unusual ones are mixed in,

33:25.570 --> 33:26.530
and their prices

33:26.770 --> 33:28.370
far exceed the market price.

33:39.550 --> 33:40.680
Here's another one.

33:41.210 --> 33:42.100
Let me see.

33:47.160 --> 33:48.270
This isn't right.

33:49.130 --> 33:49.820
This is...

33:50.450 --> 33:51.650
absurdly expensive.

33:54.070 --> 33:56.720
Logically, goods purchased
by the Services Bureau

33:56.720 --> 33:58.090
are bought in bulk,

33:58.790 --> 34:01.450
so they should be cheaper
than the market price.

34:01.610 --> 34:03.940
Instead, these prices are so much higher.

34:04.910 --> 34:05.800
Could it be...

34:05.820 --> 34:08.179
Could someone be siphoning off funds?

34:13.489 --> 34:16.489
This account statement says

34:16.810 --> 34:20.070
the Services Bureau's goods
all come from Juyun Pavilion.

34:21.630 --> 34:22.670
Ju...

34:23.360 --> 34:25.920
Is Juyun Pavilion and the Services Bureau

34:26.440 --> 34:27.770
colluding to

34:27.800 --> 34:29.600
take advantage of Qi Residence?

34:31.670 --> 34:33.880
Juyun Pavilion...

34:37.889 --> 34:38.730
Tian Xing,

34:38.750 --> 34:39.969
go over there and check

34:39.969 --> 34:41.280
if there's anything else.

34:41.280 --> 34:42.590
I'll put these statements away.

34:42.590 --> 34:45.130
-OK.
-I think we'll need them in the future.

34:48.900 --> 34:50.310
What are you looking for?

34:54.590 --> 34:55.429
Bo,

34:55.449 --> 34:56.620
it's so late.

34:57.040 --> 34:58.330
Why are you here?

34:58.360 --> 35:01.070
I didn't come for you two.

35:01.090 --> 35:01.710
I was afraid you'd...

35:01.710 --> 35:03.240
Negatively impact others.

35:03.790 --> 35:05.060
Like you said just now.

35:06.410 --> 35:07.400
But if you need

35:07.400 --> 35:08.680
my help with anything,

35:08.700 --> 35:09.630
feel free to ask.

35:11.400 --> 35:12.840
We... don't have anything

35:12.840 --> 35:14.020
we need help with.

35:14.600 --> 35:16.080
How are things on your end?

35:18.370 --> 35:20.170
Weren't you given more work

35:20.190 --> 35:21.850
because you offended Lord Lu?

35:24.410 --> 35:25.920
That little bit of work is nothing.

35:25.920 --> 35:28.000
My goal is Lord Yan Jiang.
At such a young age,

35:28.000 --> 35:29.550
he's already
a key official of Services Bureau

35:29.550 --> 35:31.510
and the governor's confidant.

35:31.760 --> 35:32.690
Without a doubt,

35:32.760 --> 35:35.760
he's the youngest high-ranking official
in history.

35:35.800 --> 35:36.400
Lord Yan Jiang

35:36.400 --> 35:37.960
is truly worthy of respect.

35:38.440 --> 35:39.330
Bo,

35:39.350 --> 35:40.510
I heard you

35:40.670 --> 35:43.480
intentionally delayed
your selection exam by a year.

35:43.480 --> 35:44.140
Yes.

35:44.550 --> 35:46.340
To pay tribute to Lord Yan Jiang,

35:46.340 --> 35:47.520
who topped the exam at 16,

35:47.520 --> 35:50.050
I waited until I was 17 to take the exam.

35:50.080 --> 35:51.710
-You're only 17 years old?
-You're only 17 years old?

35:51.710 --> 35:53.140
Yes! Don't I look it?

35:53.420 --> 35:54.220
To think that

35:54.250 --> 35:55.780
taking the exam a year later

35:55.790 --> 35:56.880
meant that the top spot

35:56.880 --> 35:58.360
would be snatched away by

35:58.360 --> 35:59.880
this clueless brat from nowhere!

35:59.880 --> 36:01.480
It seems that studying really

36:01.480 --> 36:02.930
does help a person mature.

36:02.930 --> 36:03.880
Don't just look at

36:03.880 --> 36:05.440
my sophisticated and mature exterior,

36:05.440 --> 36:07.230
but also see my firm inner heart.

36:07.230 --> 36:08.480
You've messed up the plans

36:08.480 --> 36:09.510
I've had for the past few years.

36:09.510 --> 36:11.020
But from this day forward,

36:11.050 --> 36:13.050
no one can ruin my plans again!

36:13.150 --> 36:14.400
I'll rely on my efforts to

36:14.400 --> 36:15.920
forge ahead in my official career.

36:15.920 --> 36:16.710
Do you believe in me—

36:16.710 --> 36:17.960
I know you believe in me.

36:17.960 --> 36:19.480
I bet Lord Yan Jiang believes in me too.

36:19.480 --> 36:20.370
One day,

36:20.390 --> 36:22.510
I'll be a higher official than Lord Lu!

36:22.510 --> 36:23.800
I'll scoff at him

36:23.800 --> 36:24.840
and drive him crazy with work!

36:24.840 --> 36:26.110
I'm going back to study now.

36:26.110 --> 36:26.670
Keep it up!

36:26.670 --> 36:29.070
Improve efficiency! No more night shifts!

36:29.370 --> 36:30.670
-You've got this, Bo.
-You've got this.

36:30.670 --> 36:31.850
-We have faith in you!
-Keep it up!

36:31.850 --> 36:34.740
Keep it up! Keep it up! Keep it up.

36:35.070 --> 36:36.160
Keep it up.

36:36.480 --> 36:37.600
Keep it up...

36:42.400 --> 36:43.200
Keep looking.

36:47.300 --> 36:51.110
[Respect the Wise and Welcome the Learned]

36:51.210 --> 36:54.000
[Be Proper in Attire and Conduct]

37:03.790 --> 37:05.670
Why aren't you going to work?

37:05.700 --> 37:07.630
Are you standing here to slack off?

37:10.700 --> 37:11.700
Lord Lu,

37:11.730 --> 37:14.450
we found something among the documents

37:15.030 --> 37:17.390
you asked us to sort.

37:17.980 --> 37:18.660
Go on.

37:19.200 --> 37:20.980
The items purchased by Services Bureau

37:20.980 --> 37:23.180
are priced well above the market value.

37:25.910 --> 37:27.030
What do you mean?

37:29.630 --> 37:30.630
We suspect that

37:31.630 --> 37:32.630
someone might be

37:33.550 --> 37:34.750
siphoning off funds.

37:34.800 --> 37:36.230
Yes, Lord Lu.

37:38.720 --> 37:40.510
You two sure are brazen.

37:41.510 --> 37:42.160
Fan Yun,

37:43.430 --> 37:45.680
you're just a probationary official.

37:46.310 --> 37:48.920
How dare you suspect
a senior official of my bureau?

37:48.920 --> 37:50.360
Don't you know that
slandering a Nine Cities official

37:50.360 --> 37:51.290
is a grave crime?

37:51.760 --> 37:54.110
Don't think you can do as you will

37:54.130 --> 37:56.390
just because the governor has your back.

37:56.430 --> 37:57.720
No, Lord Lu.

37:57.740 --> 37:58.690
-No?
-I...

37:59.360 --> 38:01.220
Do you have conclusive evidence?

38:02.010 --> 38:03.120
Last night, we checked

38:03.120 --> 38:04.850
the Services Bureau's ledger.

38:07.620 --> 38:08.660
Utter rubbish!

38:09.190 --> 38:11.230
The documents I asked you to sort

38:11.250 --> 38:13.310
doesn't include my bureau's ledger.

38:13.780 --> 38:14.620
Besides,

38:15.410 --> 38:17.090
how can the items of the estate

38:17.420 --> 38:19.380
be measured by the market price?

38:20.400 --> 38:21.510
Do not mention this

38:22.030 --> 38:23.520
to anyone else again.

38:24.190 --> 38:26.390
Now, step back and go clean the latrine!

38:27.200 --> 38:28.910
Yes, Lord Lu.

38:30.890 --> 38:31.710
Go now!

38:36.290 --> 38:37.210
Lord Cai.

38:48.390 --> 38:50.450
What were those two doing here again?

38:51.040 --> 38:52.000
They said that

38:52.020 --> 38:53.750
while sorting documents here,

38:53.940 --> 38:56.110
they found our Services Bureau's ledger.

38:56.110 --> 38:58.040
They even said it was problematic.

38:58.040 --> 39:00.070
Found our bureau's ledger?

39:01.070 --> 39:02.150
How could she

39:02.150 --> 39:04.210
have possibly found our ledger?

39:04.240 --> 39:06.040
Right? Our bureau's ledger

39:06.080 --> 39:07.940
couldn't be among the documents.

39:08.080 --> 39:10.930
They also said
the purchased items were priced

39:10.960 --> 39:12.590
well above the market value.

39:12.630 --> 39:14.370
What a load of nonsense!

39:23.440 --> 39:24.160
Tian Xing,

39:24.500 --> 39:26.580
don't you think this is a bit strange?

39:27.550 --> 39:29.280
Since Lord Lu denied it flatly,

39:29.480 --> 39:31.190
there must be more to it.

39:33.190 --> 39:34.060
Also,

39:34.430 --> 39:36.580
did you see the teapot on Lord Lu's desk

39:36.850 --> 39:37.800
just now?

39:41.740 --> 39:43.010
Lord Lu might be the one

39:43.040 --> 39:44.330
who sends us tea

39:44.580 --> 39:45.680
every day.

39:48.320 --> 39:49.520
How is that possible?

39:50.830 --> 39:53.380
I just think that some things

39:53.510 --> 39:54.800
might not be exactly

39:54.800 --> 39:55.770
as they seem.

39:56.720 --> 39:58.280
Some people appear harsh

39:58.680 --> 40:00.940
but actually have profound intentions.

40:01.150 --> 40:03.580
Some things seem chaotic

40:03.610 --> 40:04.960
on the surface,

40:05.190 --> 40:07.350
but actually hold hidden truths.

40:10.730 --> 40:11.260
Let's go.

40:11.630 --> 40:12.350
We have to leave the estate.

40:12.350 --> 40:13.270
What for?

40:14.370 --> 40:15.440
To find evidence.

40:15.460 --> 40:16.720
Didn't Lord Lu tell us

40:16.940 --> 40:17.940
to find evidence?

40:18.440 --> 40:19.280
OK.

40:19.770 --> 40:21.560
Since all the items
on the problematic statements

40:21.560 --> 40:23.620
were purchased from Juyun Pavilion,

40:23.760 --> 40:24.960
we could clarify things

40:24.960 --> 40:26.840
if we could find and ask the manager

40:26.840 --> 40:27.900
of Juyun Pavilion.

40:28.280 --> 40:29.740
But where's this manager?

40:30.880 --> 40:31.960
Just follow me.

40:33.540 --> 40:38.760
[Yong City]

40:58.320 --> 40:59.210
Mother.

40:59.910 --> 41:00.890
Mother.

41:12.160 --> 41:12.960
Mother?

41:13.510 --> 41:14.450
Mother!

41:29.700 --> 41:30.670
Your guest has arrived.

41:30.670 --> 41:31.710
Have a good chat.

41:35.340 --> 41:36.440
Young Master Qiyan.

41:36.440 --> 41:38.900
Where'd you find the time
to have tea with me?

41:40.480 --> 41:41.690
Who is this?

41:43.290 --> 41:45.550
Lou Qiyan, President of Juyun Pavilion.

41:46.440 --> 41:47.970
Hello, Young Master Qiyan.

41:50.250 --> 41:51.380
Go ahead. What is it?

41:53.540 --> 41:54.670
Young Master Qiyan,

41:54.920 --> 41:56.020
take a look at these.

41:56.020 --> 41:57.510
Are the goods listed here

41:57.960 --> 41:59.420
from your Juyun Pavilion?

42:07.760 --> 42:08.560
That's right.

42:10.000 --> 42:11.160
Are the prices

42:11.320 --> 42:12.640
consistent with

42:12.920 --> 42:14.450
these account statements?

42:15.890 --> 42:16.770
Yes, they are.

42:19.550 --> 42:20.880
But Young Master Qiyan,

42:20.990 --> 42:23.450
are these goods really that expensive?

42:28.880 --> 42:29.550
So you two are

42:29.550 --> 42:30.880
here to interrogate me.

42:32.470 --> 42:33.800
If you don't believe me,

42:33.910 --> 42:35.410
you can come with me
to Juyun Pavilion.

42:35.410 --> 42:36.640
Corroborating the ledgers

42:36.640 --> 42:38.170
will clear things right up.

42:41.510 --> 42:43.890
Since you're so broad-minded,

42:44.320 --> 42:45.040
why don't we

42:45.190 --> 42:46.670
make a trip there?
